Partner checked for a major, then chose three notrump, so you have around 28 combined points and stoppers in every suit. Nine tricks is the target. This is the classic hold-up shape: East has the \HKQ and five hearts, West only two, and your lone heart guard is the \HA.
[ROLE declarer][STAGE auction-end]
